Text: Buy this album! If you download it and like it then buy it! Support the Swedish Metal

Bockar och tackar för denna torrent :D

It went like 10 seconds in to the first song, then something happend.... I herd the best metall ive´d ever herd!! Download this torrent and buy the album, otherwise they wont produce any more of this excellent melodic heavy metall!! Damn its good!!
